keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

#unmappings

#vomnibar in bookmarks 
unmap b  
unmap B

#make space for tab moving
unmap a
unmap s




map h goBack
map l goForward
map gj goUp
map z scrollDown
map c scrollUp
map a previousTab
map s  nextTab 
map w visitPreviousTab
map q moveTabLeft
map e moveTabRight
